would live forever.

01:07:17.800 --> 01:07:20.040
Do you believe this could be true?

01:07:20.360 --> 01:07:23.520
Ronnie Defeo came to me
weeks before the murders...

01:07:23.680 --> 01:07:28.520
...and he spoke about hearing voices
and seeing things in the house.

01:07:29.080 --> 01:07:31.240
I didn't believe him until yesterday.

01:07:33.160 --> 01:07:37.440
Mrs. Lutz, get you and your family
out of that house...

01:07:37.600 --> 01:07:38.880
...right now.

01:07:51.760 --> 01:07:52.920
- Hello?
<i>- George. </i>

01:07:53.080 --> 01:07:55.280
<i>George, I've just been to see</i>
<i>Father Callaway. </i>

01:07:55.440 --> 01:07:58.320
<i>Listen to me, you gotta get you</i>
<i>and the kids out of the house. </i>

01:07:59.440 --> 01:08:00.840
<i>George?</i>

01:08:02.120 --> 01:08:03.600
<i>Are you there? George?</i>

01:08:16.600 --> 01:08:20.840
Billy! Michael! Where's George?

01:08:21.000 --> 01:08:23.040
He's in the boathouse.

01:08:40.000 --> 01:08:43.120
George, we have
to get out of here now.

01:08:43.279 --> 01:08:44.800
George!

01:09:23.000 --> 01:09:24.840
Are you fucking crazy, George?

01:09:25.080 --> 01:09:26.600
Have you lost your mind?

01:09:26.760 --> 01:09:28.240
You tried to kill me.

01:09:33.279 --> 01:09:36.000
- Chelsea!
- Mommy! Mommy!

01:09:36.160 --> 01:09:37.479
I'm down here, Mommy!

01:09:38.760 --> 01:09:41.200
Chelsea, honey,
what are you doing down here?

01:10:08.200 --> 01:10:09.760
I think she misses her daddy.

01:10:12.920 --> 01:10:14.440
Don't you?

01:10:15.760 --> 01:10:17.520
Give me back my daughter.

01:10:22.960 --> 01:10:26.680
I wanna talk to you. Wait.
I wanna talk to you!

01:10:27.480 --> 01:10:29.840
Kids, get down here, now!

01:10:30.000 --> 01:10:31.760
Kids, get down here!

01:10:31.920 --> 01:10:34.160
- Billy, help me push this!
- Mom, where are you going?

01:10:37.560 --> 01:10:39.040
Billy!

01:10:40.240 --> 01:10:41.440
- Hurry. Go.
- Billy!

01:10:43.000 --> 01:10:44.720
Mom, why are you wet?

01:10:46.000 --> 01:10:48.160
Mommy! Mommy!

01:10:50.240 --> 01:10:51.960
Come on, Mom!

01:10:53.400 --> 01:10:54.680
Hurry.

01:10:55.400 --> 01:10:57.720
Billy, come on!

01:11:11.480 --> 01:11:13.080
Run! Go, go, go!

01:11:15.800 --> 01:11:17.360
You're stuck! You're stuck!

01:11:17.760 --> 01:11:19.320
Stay here!

01:11:21.800 --> 01:11:22.960
Great!

01:11:23.800 --> 01:11:27.440
Let go of my mom, you bastard!
Let go right now! Let go.

01:11:31.800 --> 01:11:34.400
- What the hell is your problem?
- Let's go.

01:11:35.360 --> 01:11:37.040
These kids are out of control.

01:11:39.640 --> 01:11:42.320
- Mom, it's stuck!
- It won't open!

01:11:44.520 --> 01:11:46.280
Where's Chelsea? Chelsea!

01:11:59.240 --> 01:12:03.520
- Hurry, hurry, Billy. Hurry.
- Come on. Let's go. Be quiet, be quiet.

01:12:46.440 --> 01:12:48.240
Billy!

01:13:32.120 --> 01:13:34.320
I want you to hold on tight.

01:13:44.680 --> 01:13:46.320
Jump, baby.

01:13:48.600 --> 01:13:49.880
- Come on, honey.
- Come on.

01:13:50.040 --> 01:13:51.560
- Come on, Michael.
- No, Mommy.

01:13:51.760 --> 01:13:53.680
- No.
- Hurry, baby.

01:13:54.600 --> 01:13:56.920
Come on, Michael.
Come on, Michael.

01:13:58.040 --> 01:13:59.720
- Come on, hurry.
- Let's get out of here.

01:14:02.440 --> 01:14:04.880
- Come here. Come here.
- No.

01:14:07.560 --> 01:14:09.800
You leave him alone.

01:14:13.760 --> 01:14:15.280
<i>Kill them. </i>

01:14:16.120 --> 01:14:17.800
Don't hurt him!

01:14:19.720 --> 01:14:21.800
Back the fuck up!

01:15:02.000 --> 01:15:03.360
<i>Kill them. </i>

01:15:11.000 --> 01:15:13.600
Hurry. Let's grab some rope.

01:15:15.480 --> 01:15:17.280
<i>Kill them. </i>

01:15:35.160 --> 01:15:37.920
Kathy, kill me!

01:15:38.600 --> 01:15:40.560
You kill me, or I'll kill you!

01:15:40.840 --> 01:15:43.000
Nobody's dying today.

01:16:04.000 --> 01:16:06.760
Okay, let's get him in the boat.

01:16:29.920 --> 01:16:32.000
Why are we taking him?
Let's just leave him here.

01:16:32.160 --> 01:16:35.400
I can't explain it to you right now. We
have to get him away from the house.

01:17:31.800 --> 01:17:33.840
Don't even look at it, Kathy.

01:17:34.080 --> 01:17:35.520
Let's get out of here.

